# Build context is the repo root; trim everything we don't need.
# Only packages/protocol-core/{src,package.json,tsconfig*.json},
# packages/daemon/{src,package.json,tsconfig*.json}, and e2b/entrypoint.sh
# are actually referenced by e2b.Dockerfile.

# VCS + tooling
.git
.gitignore
.github
.claude
.vscode
.idea

# Anything that isn't packages/* or e2b/
backend
frontend
cli
e2e
docs
scripts
infrastructure
Makefile
README.md
CLAUDE.md
*.md

# Per-package noise
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/.cache
**/coverage
**/__pycache__
**/.venv
**/.pytest_cache

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp
